<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.1.6">
<l>ñālamellā mamutuceytu nāṉmaṟaiyum toṭarāta</l>
<l>pālakaṉā yālilaiyil paḷḷikoḷḷum paramaṉiṭam</l>
<l>cālivaḷam perukivarun taṭamaṇṇit teṉkaraimēl</l>
<l>cēlukaḷum vayalnāṅkait tiruttēva ṉārtokaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of the supreme who slept on a banyan leaf as a babe,</l>
<l>Having consumed all the worlds, who is unattainable</l>
<l rend="indent">even through the four Vedas,</l>
<l>Is Tiruttēvaṉārtokai in Nāṅkai with paddy fields where carp leap,</l>
<l>On the southern shore of the wide Maṇṇi [River]</l>
<l rend="indent">which comes increasing the abundance of the paddy.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
